{
  "texts": [
    "Some present tools for distributed computing are too low-phase or not flexible enough to be adjusted to requirements [27,28].",
    "Many technologies generate a great base for building higher-level distributed computing ecosystems [29,30].",
    "Also, Machine learning (ML), a subsection of Artificial Intelligence (AI), has become a strong tool for several bioinformatics uses [31,32].",
    "Depending on big datasets, ML mechanisms are particularly suitable for forecasting and pattern recognition [33].",
    "There are some emerging uses of ML within the bioinformatics area."
  ]
}